#compdef ohrun
# Documentation: https://github.com/humarf/OHsentinel/wiki/OHcli
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-19
# Verified: no canonical upstream CLI named "ohrun" found via web search.
# STUB: provides only generic --help/--version completion. The previously
# claimed OpenHPI flags were unsupported by any primary source.

_arguments -s -S \
  '(- *)'{-h,--help}'[show help]' \
  '(- *)'{-V,--version}'[show version]' \
  '*::arguments:_default'
